name: average-daily-footfall-in-aviation-house-by-week
title: Average Daily Footfall In Aviation House By Week
description: This dataset shows the daily average of FSA staff entering Aviation House by week. The weekly total number of FSA Staff entering Aviation House is divided by 5 to give the daily average.
